statements.sql: select `winners`.*, `game_prize`.`prize_amount` as `prize_amount`, `prizes`.`name` as `prize_name`, `users`.`name` as `user_name` from `winners` inner join `game_prize` on `winners`.`game_prize_id` = `game_prize`.`id` inner join `prizes` on `game_prize`.`prize_id` = `prizes`.`id` left join `users` on `winners`.`user_id` = `users`.`id`

select * from `winners` inner join `game_prize` on `winners`.`game_prize_id` = `game_prize`.`id` inner join `prizes` on `game_prize`.`prize_id` = `prizes`.`id` inner join `users` on `winners`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` where `user_id` is not null and `ticket_id` is not null and `claim_id` is not null

select `claims`.`id` as `claim_id`, `claims`.`ticket_id`, `claims`.`game_prize_id`, `claims`.`status`, `claims`.`comment`, `claims`.`created_at`, `game_prize`.*, `tickets`.`object`, `users`.`name` as `user_name`, `prizes`.`name` as `prize_name` from `claims` inner join `game_prize` on `claims`.`game_prize_id` = `game_prize`.`prize_id` inner join `tickets` on `claims`.`ticket_id` = `tickets`.`id` inner join `users` on `tickets`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` inner join `games` on `tickets`.`game_id` = `games`.`id` inner join `prizes` on `game_prize`.`prize_id` = `prizes`.`id` where `games`.`id` = 2 and `claims`.`status` = 'Open'
select distinct `users`.`id`, `users`.`name`, `users`.`email` from `sessions` left join `users` on `sessions`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` where `user_id` is not null
select `game_prize`.*, `prizes`.`name` from `game_prize` left join `prizes` on `game_prize`.`prize_id` = `prizes`.`id` where `game_prize`.`quantity` > '0' and `game_prize`.`game_id` = 2

select `winners`.*, `game_prize`.`prize_amount` as `prize_amount`, `prizes`.`name` as `prize_name`, `users`.`name` as `user_name` from `winners` inner join `game_prize` on `winners`.`game_prize_id` = `game_prize`.`id` inner join `prizes` on `game_prize`.`prize_id` = `prizes`.`id` left join `users` on `winners`.`user_id` = `users`.`id` where `user_id` is null and `ticket_id` is null and `claim_id` is null
